Package ca.ualberta.ishelf.Models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    Book class Signatures created by Jeremy -edited Mehrab
    Borrow
    THis is the borrow object which deals with the borrow transaction
    Database
    Database object used as an interface between our applications and our Firebase Real-Time database Important Note: Any method that gets an object from the firebase will not work due to the nature of threads.
    Notification
    The Notification is used to store all the information relevent to a single notification.
    Rating
    THis is the Wow factor rating object, which deals with the star rating of an User or Book object.
    Request
    A request object represents one user requesting to borrow a book from its owner A request will always be stored under the owners User object, so we only need to store the requesters username Status is used to represent whether a request has been accepted, declined, or if no action has been taken yet Since these objects are not directly stored in firebase, they don't need a unique id
